data.description: So much charm & character in this adorable 3 bedroom,2.5 bath home!Originally built in 1910,the home was moved to this lot & renovated in 1989.Some original features remain,such as the gorgeous wood double doors leading to the master bedroom,hardwood floors in foyer & middle hallway,12+ ft. ceilings & brick fireplace in living room (decorative only).New carpet in front living room & bedrooms.Open concept back den gives a view of the breakfast area & kitchen & overlooks back yard through 3 floor to ceiling windows!All kitchen appliances included!New toilets & flooring in all baths & new shower unit in guest bath!New back deck off den.Paved circular driveway.Full length covered front porch.Shady lot w/ no grass maintenance.Storage area in walk-in crawl space.
